<div id="ver1" style="display: none;">
<p>Students can obtain enrollment verifications free of charge through <strong>National Student Clearinghouse Student Self-Service</strong>. This enables students to go online, day or night, and print enrollment certificates that can be provided to third parties, as requested.</p>
<p>To obtain a verification of enrollment, follow these steps:</p>
<ol start="1">
<li>Log in at&nbsp;<a href="http://my.byui.edu"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">my.byui.edu.</span></a></li>
<li>Click on the blue Student tab</li>
<li>Scroll to Related Links at the bottom on the right</li>
<li>Select Enrollment Verification under Academic Resources</li>
<li>You can choose enrollment for the current semester or every semester attended</li>
</ol>
<p>Students can also access the verification site directly at <a href="http://www.byui.edu/verification"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">www.byui.edu/verification</span></a>.</p>
</div>
<div id="ver2" style="display: none;">
<p>Students can obtain Good Student Discount certificates free of charge through <strong>National Student Clearinghouse Student Self-Service</strong>. This enables students to go online, day or night, and print enrollment certificates that can be provided to third parties, as requested.</p>
<p>To obtain a Good Student Discount certificate, follow these steps:</p>
<ol start="1">
<li>Log in at <a href="http://my.byui.edu"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">my.byui.edu</span></a></li>
<li>Click on the blue Student tab</li>
<li>Scroll to Related Links at the bottom on the right</li>
<li>Select Enrollment Verification under Academic Resources</li>
<li>You can choose enrollment for the current semester or every semester attended</li>
</ol>
<p>Students can also access the verification site directly at <a href="http://www.byui.edu/verification"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">www.byui.edu/verification</span></a>.</p>
</div>
<div id="ver3" style="display: none;">
<p>If you are in the Military or a dependent of someone in the Military and need proof of enrollment, please email <a href="mailto:verifications@byui.edu"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">verifications@byui.edu</span></a>.</p>
<p>You will need to include the following in the email:</p>
<ul>
<li>Name</li>
<li>I-Number</li>
<li>Anticipated graduation date</li>
<li>Return email where you want the verification emailed to</li>
<li>Any other specific information you need to be included</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div id="ver4" style="display: none;">
<p>If you need to have a Canadian form completed, please bring it to the Student Records and Registration Office in Kimball 190. Please allow 24 business hours for our office to complete the form. We will also need the following information:</p>
<ul>
<li>Name</li>
<li>I-Number</li>
<li>Anticipated graduation date</li>
<li>Semesters for which the form needs to be completed</li>
<li>Any other specific information you need to be included</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div id="ver5" style="display: none;">
<p>For Alaskan students needing a PFD form completed, please email <a href="mailto:verifications@byui.edu"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">verifications@byui.edu</span></a> with your request and the blank form. You may also bring the form into our office in Kimball 190. Please allow 24 hours for our office to complete the PFD form and provide us with the following information:</p>
<ul>
<li>Name</li>
<li>I-Number</li>
<li>Return email address</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div id="ver6" style="display: none;">
<p>International Students will need to obtain a manual enrollment verification by emailing <a href="mailto:verifications@byui.edu"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">verifications@byui.edu</span></a>. Please include the following information:</p>
<ul>
<li>Name</li>
<li>I-Number</li>
<li>Anticipated graduation date</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div id="ver7" style="display: none;">
<p>Parents and third parties can access student enrollment information for a nominal fee through Enrollment Verify. Requesters can obtain individual verifications for $2.50 or set up a subscriber account. (BYU&ndash;Idaho does not impose an additional surcharge for this service.)</p>
<p>To obtain an enrollment verification, follow these steps:</p>
<ol start="1">
<li>Go to <a href="http://www.studentclearinghouse.org"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">www.studentclearinghouse.org</span>.</a></li>
<li>Select &ldquo;Verify Current Enrollment.&rdquo;</li>
<li>Read and accept the EnrollmentVerify terms and conditions.</li>
<li>Search for and select &ldquo;Brigham Young University&ndash;Idaho.&rdquo;</li>
<li>Enter the student&rsquo;s name and date of birth.</li>
<li>Enter your payment information.</li>
<li>Receive and print the enrollment verification.</li>
</ol></div>
<div id="ver8" style="display: none;">
<p>If needed, an <span style="text-decoration: underline;">official letter</span> can also be printed to include with your NSC document verifying that NSC is BYU-Idaho's authorized certifying agent. If you have other questions regarding enrollment verifications, contact Student Records and Registration at <a href="mailto:verifications@byui.edu"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">verifications@byui.edu</span></a> or (208) 496-1000.</p>
</div>
